Responsibilities
Assist in purchase coordination, prepare business analysis reports & sales forecast;
Analyze business trends and consumer insights to deliver brand sales and market share targets;
Assist in product & category management;
Ensure inventory levels of various product categories are controlled within reasonable size during both slack and peak seasons;
Coordinate with internal and external parties to maintain daily operation and maximize business opportunities;
